            "title": "地產｜恒地(00012)首匯料下周上樓書",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"地產｜恒地(00012)首匯料下周上樓書\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">地產｜恒地(00012)首匯料下周上樓書</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恒地(00012)發展的紅磡首匯蓄勢推售，恒基物業代理董事及營業(一)部總經理<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:林達民;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/林達民\">林達民</a>指出，首匯預計下周上載樓書，很大機會下月發售。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">林達民指出，除首匯，該部今年有機會推出土瓜灣壹沐2期(約410伙)、油麻地廟街重建項目(約48伙)，以及古洞北項目(約682伙)和必嘉坊第6期(約200伙)。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">林達民表示，該部今年截至2月26日售出約240伙，套現逾40億元，當中必嘉坊系列已推出共4期，由開售至今共售出約1340伙，套現約70億元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他指出，必嘉坊．迎匯過去有部分單位轉租，當中約70至80伙的租約預計今年及明年到期，該部部署把相關單位交吉出售。</p></div>",
